drawnet.lib.solvers
Class Exec

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.solvers.Exec

public class Exec
extends java.lang.Object

A class that runs external processes. You can run a program 4 ways:

  • exec: execute the command and returns immediately.
  • execWait: execute the command and don't return until the command finishes.
  • execPrint: execute the command and print the output.
  • execPrintAndWait: execute the command, print the output and wait until the command finishes.
The full command path must be specified; shell commands will not work.
